name: PancakeLock
description: Pancakelock is an autonomous, frictionless, and decentralized application that aims to bring greater security and legality of operations to the applications built on Binance Smart Chain protocol. The Pancakelock will utilize the BSC to create a full-stack liquidity lock system that allows developers and token holders and to lock their BEP 20 tokens and Liquidity tokens in a smart contract vault and earn $PLOCK token for using the platform.
